2d57173f-6695-487f-9ea7-7a2a09467955.do_description: To make the output, you have to...draw a light blue line to connect any dark blue squares that are on the same line or row.
2d57173f-6695-487f-9ea7-7a2a09467955.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input grid.

df0f0af2-63f6-4fd1-9288-604a07e4f7b8.see_description: In the input, you should see...several dark blue blocks.
